Trinity::

She kept going inside, but could still see the entrance.  She sniffed 
around and found the source of the death smell. There were old 
remains of animals and bots in a pile in a corner of the cave. She 
put her paw up to her nose as the smell was over whelming. She walked 
backward and bumped into something. She slowly turned around and saw 
as metal skeleton of a bot standing up against the wall.  It started 
to fall towards her as she bumped it.  She screamed at the top of her 
little lungs and ran out of the cave.  She stood outside the cave, 
her face pale and her little lungs going into hyperdrive.
